      • updateDice

        public void updateDice(String raspberryId,
                       int update)
                throws RaspberryService.RaspberryNotFoundException
        Calls the diceUpdate method on the game that is registered for the given raspberry. If the raspberry is not registered to a game, nothing happens.
        Parameters:
        raspberryId - the raspberry which sends the update
        update - the facet number of the update
        Throws:
        RaspberryService.RaspberryNotFoundException - if the raspberry does not exist.

      • updateDiceBatteryStatus

        public void updateDiceBatteryStatus(String raspberryId,
                                    int batteryStatus)
                             throws RaspberryService.RaspberryNotFoundException
        Method that updates the batteryStatus of a Dice if a game is registered to it.
        Parameters:
        raspberryId - id of the raspberry that sent the update.
        batteryStatus - new battery level in percent
        Throws:
        RaspberryService.RaspberryNotFoundException - if the raspberry is not registered

      • updateDiceConnectionStatus

        public boolean updateDiceConnectionStatus(String raspberryId,
                                          boolean connectionStatus)
                                   throws RaspberryService.RaspberryNotFoundException
        Method that updates the connectionStatus of a Dice if a game is registered to it. If not it returns false.
        Parameters:
        raspberryId - id of the raspberry that sent the update.
        connectionStatus - new connection status.
        Returns:
        true if raspberry is in a game, false if not.
        Throws:
        RaspberryService.RaspberryNotFoundException - if the raspberry is not registered.

      • registerGame

        public void registerGame(String raspberryID,
                         Game game)
                  throws RaspberryService.RaspberryAlreadyInUseException,
                         RaspberryService.RaspberryNotFoundException
        Method that registers a game for a given raspberry id.
        Parameters:
        raspberryID - id of the raspberry the game should be associated with.
        game - the game that gets registered.
        Throws:
        RaspberryService.RaspberryAlreadyInUseException - when raspberry is already assigned to a running game.
        RaspberryService.RaspberryNotFoundException
